{
 "name": "RPlog_Revisiting_Colonel_Virda",
 "title": "Revisiting Colonel Virda",
 "summary": "In the Colonel's office at CorSec Station 17 in Coronet City during the Imperial occupation of Corellia, the on-edge Twila chafes under the COMPNOR and ISB officials breathing down her neck since the lockdown began. The station, nominally CorSec but in truth run by ISB and CompForce muscle, becomes the stage for a tense encounter as the Sith Lord Malign, going by Tyler, arrives with the officer Korynn and Pen. The cold machinery of Imperial control looms over the proceedings as the players navigate the occupied station's dangerous politics.",
